<div class="full-menu">
	<div class="inner">
		<div class="charter-menu color1">
			<div class="co-icon">
				<%=image_tag('dolphin.png', class: 'icon') %>
			</div>

			<div class="text">
				<h4>Sightseeing</h4>
				<div class="title-line"></div>
				<div class="clearfix"></div>

      	<p>There are plenty of interesting things to see while on the water, including dolphins, sea turtles, beautiful homes and boats.</p>
				<a class="book-btn">Book Now</a>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="charter-menu color2">
			<div class="co-icon">
				<%=image_tag('cocktail.png', class: 'icon') %>
			</div>

			<div class="text">
				<h4>Booze Cruises</h4>
				<div class="title-line"></div>
				<div class="clearfix"></div>

				<p>BYOB! Spend the day relaxing on the water. There are also plenty of fun restaurants/bars in the area to make a quick stop for a bushwacker!</p>
				<a class="book-btn">Book Now</a>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="charter-menu color3">
			<div class="co-icon">
				<%=image_tag('sunbathe.png', class: 'icon') %>
			</div>

			<div class="text">
				<h4>Island Hopping</h4>
				<div class="title-line"></div>
				<div class="clearfix"></div>

				<p>The area has plenty of islands in the back bays to pull up in the boat and hangout. The water is shallow and calm, perfect for kids to play!</p>
				<a class="book-btn">Book Now</a>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="charter-menu color4">
			<div class="co-icon">
				<%=image_tag('tropical.png', class: 'icon') %>
			</div>

			<div class="text">
				<h4>Sunset Cruises</h4>
				<div class="title-line"></div>
				<div class="clearfix"></div>

				<p>This is the best time of day to be on the water! You can’t beat watching the sunset from the boat!</p>
				<a class="book-btn">Book Now</a>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="charter-menu color5">
			<div class="co-icon">
				<%=image_tag('jets.png', class: 'icon') %>
			</div>

			<div class="text">
				<h4>Blue Angel Practice*</h4>
				<div class="title-line"></div>
				<div class="clearfix"></div>

				<p>This is a full day, special charter to Pensacola pass to watch the famous U.S. Navy Blue Angels practice. It is a great way to see them perform their tricks without the crowds, and while hanging out at the beach!</p>
				<p><span>*This charter is weather dependent, and available only on days the Blue Angels practice: <br> April, May, July, August, September – Tuesdays and Wednesdays.</span></p>
				<!-- <a class="book-btn">Book Now</a> -->
			</div>
		</div>

	</div>
</div>

<div class="callout">
	<div class="inner">
		<div class="text-blk">
			<h4>Out of town friends:</h4>
			<p>We understand that you are here to create wonderful memories with your family and friends. We want to show you the other side of Orange Beach, AL and how the locals enjoy the area by water. Let us help you have a perfect and FUN day on the water with no worries or stress!</p>
		</div>

		<div class="text-blk">
			<h4>Locals:</h4>
				<p>We are here for you too! Have family or friends in town and want to show them a good time on the water but you do not have a boat? Or, maybe you do not want the stress of driving a boat and trying to entertain your family and friends? We can help! Give us a call today at (251-424-3430) and be sure to ask for a local’s discount!</p>
		</div>

		<div class="text-blk">
			<h4>Celebrating? </h4>
			<p>A PRIVATE boat charter is the perfect way to celebrate an anniversary, a graduation, a birthday, or anything else you might be celebrating!</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>




